{"tid":1802120,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"用M記嘅鹽自制成日缺貨嘅生理鹽水","createTime":"2019-12-29T07:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-29T09:35:17.000Z","uid":338276,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"32f47a6e47c494e28eaf50f2d0e8710075fb3ae0","tid":1802120,"uid":338276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-29T07:53:23.000Z","msg":"自6月開始，次次去藥房都買唔到大枝生理鹽水，自制定帶出街又怕有菌，終於決定試吓用M記嘅細包鹽。<br />\n<br />\n首先，生理鹽水大概係0.8% 到 0.9% 嘅鹽水，即100g (或ml, 因為係水) 入面有0.8 - 0.9g 鹽。<br />\n<br />\n今日磅咗5包M記嘅鹽，平均每包係0.774g，如果只係外用清洗，每100ml 水放一包都好接近0.8% saline solution.  雖然M記嘅鹽唔係NaCl,  但外用叫做好過清水，而且就算畀人查，帶住包M記嘅鹽佢無得入你，自己喺屋企包一小袋鹽反而佢話懷疑你藏毒都得。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，500ml嘅蒸餾水加5包M記嘅鹽就得。<br />\n<br />\n磅鹽結果如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/k29Rgrr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fk29Rgrr.jpg&h=5b3752bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e2aUec8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe2aUec8.jpg&h=84f36664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tf9Nzda.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftf9Nzda.jpg&h=f970d6a5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g3bHn6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg3bHn6w.jpg&h=9a6f0fff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wFnSLjT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwFnSLjT.jpg&h=7becf630&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sU4mDEU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsU4mDEU.jpg&h=45e86c50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jaDiFTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjaDiFTg.jpg&h=a6f908bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/76czedh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F76czedh.jpg&h=4a377843&s={SIZE}\" /><b